{"tid":2249194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港天橋塗鴉 聲援「奶茶盟友」","createTime":"2020-10-19T07:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T08:16:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5af29a62367a1a6d659a60bad6496456c43df1","tid":2249194,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/KQDRMUBUMFDZBII7GQ6EJ25PX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FKQDRMUBUMFDZBII7GQ6EJ25PX4%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=f53043e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FKQDRMUBUMFDZBII7GQ6EJ25PX4%2F&h=163d6589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/KQDRMUBUMFDZBII7GQ6EJ25PX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港天橋塗鴉 聲援「奶茶盟友」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7qE6vApWEYI9ECw0qfhSVxcoqEk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y6TXGCIMORDWDAQE3QSMWD5HG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7qE6vApWEYI9ECw0qfhSVxcoqEk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY6TXGCIMORDWDAQE3QSMWD5HG4.jpg&h=f8dd7f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■康山道天橋出現「#StandWithThailand」。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12港人被中國秘密扣押近兩個月，至今仍音訊全無。香港監察（Hong Kong Watch）創辦人羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）及「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」顧問邵嵐日前發起一人一相網上行動，手持寫上「#save12hkyouths」標籤，呼籲國際社會關注12名港人，連日來多名社運及知名人士陸續上傳「#save12hkyouths」標籤的自拍照。太古康山道天橋昨日亦有人噴上「#save12hkyouths」字句，不少途人經過拍照並上傳至社交網站。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：抗爭者促德禁泰王旅居  君主制爭拗 泰爆兩代撕裂<br />\n<br />\n同一天橋亦有「#StandWithThailand」字句，聲援泰國反政府的示威者。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A__zAW5_ahBq3KKp9C68X43ePxA=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CFK5WLOWYVD2DCGWFJXRPKBMAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA__zAW5_ahBq3KKp9C68X43ePxA%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCFK5WLOWYVD2DCGWFJXRPKBMAI.jpg&h=58fbcaee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■同一天橋亦噴上「#save12hkyouths」，關注被送中港人。"},{"pid":"104906994395e20b806e0abf5829884f05279da2","tid":2249194,"uid":125553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:48:14.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒：泰國網民無法聯署，由奶茶聯盟接手聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2248818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2248818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒fb：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3434464546646029/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F3434464546646029%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=45b2f076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3434464546646029/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【泰國網民無法聯署，由奶茶聯盟接手聯署】<br />\n<br />\n自從泰國網民在「<a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8872039f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a>」發起聯署批評泰國皇室，要求推進民主改革，泰國政府下令所有國內互聯網供應商禁止用戶訪問「<a href=\"http://Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FChange.org&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=66dfdaf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Change.org</a>」。<br />\n<br />\n當極權政府打壓人民，甚至行使封鎖互聯網資訊流通的做法，作為擁抱自由的盟友，是時候幫忙廣傳，呼籲各位參與聯署！<br />\n<br />\n聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/สภาสหพันธ์สาธารณรัฐเยอรมนี-ให้วชิราลงกรณ์เป็นบุคคลที่ไม่เป็นที่ยอมรับทางการทูต-deutscher-bundestag-declare-vajiralonkorn-persona-non-grata\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2F%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%A0%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%AB%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%98%E0%B9%8C%E0%B8%AA%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%98%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%93%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%90%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%B5-%E0%B9%83%E0%B8%AB%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%8A%E0%B8%B4%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%93%E0%B9%8C%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%B8%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%84%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%88%E0%B9%84%E0%B8%A1%E0%B9%88%E0%B9%80%E0%B8%9B%E0%B9%87%E0%B8%99%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B5%E0%B9%88%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%AD%E0%B8%A1%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%97%E0%B8%B9%E0%B8%95-deutscher-bundestag-declare-vajiralonkorn-persona-non-grata&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=a7af6c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/สภาสหพันธ์สาธารณรัฐเยอรมนี-ให้วชิราลงกรณ์เป็นบุคคลที่ไม่เป็นที่ยอมรับทางการทูต-deutscher-bundestag-declare-vajiralonkorn-persona-non-grata</a><br />\n<br />\n#StandWithThailand<br />\n#MilkTeaAlliance"},{"pid":"e3804f82acd01d09b059ad9fb7b54eb46686da92","tid":2249194,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4644e0340a08fa130a6f663780b01ab347b5c2f5","tid":2249194,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d5af29a62367a1a6d659a60bad6496456c43df1","tid":2249194,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T07:32:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/KQDRMUBUMFDZBII7GQ6EJ25PX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FKQDRMUBUMFDZBII7GQ6EJ25PX4%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=f53043e0\